data.description: Welcome to this exceptional 2-family home located at the Bronx, offering a total of 7 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms. NEW ROOF, NEW HOT WATER TANK. Finished basement: Huge recreation room, Boiler room, Full bathroom, basement front garage. The first floor, spanning 1,134 square feet, features 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. The second floor, also 1,134 square feet, comprises 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. Sitting on a generous lot measuring 25x100 and a spacious building size of 21x54, this property offers ample space for comfortable living. Conveniently located just a 5-minute walk from the Bx40/Bx42 bus stop, commuting is a breeze.
